e type strain).</s></p><p class="description"><s>The chemotaxonomic and general characteristics are the same as given above for the genus.</s><s>Grows between 15 and 37 °C and at pH 4.5–7.2.</s><s>Does not grow on 2 % NaCl.</s><s>Predominant fatty acids are ai-C<sub>17 : 0</sub> and i-C<sub>16 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The G+C content of DNA of the type strain is 71.9 mol%.</s></p><p class="description"><s>The type strain, Delta3<sup>T</sup> (=DSM 45228<sup>T</sup> =NBRC 104875<sup>T</sup>), was isolated from a soil sample from an undefined location in Cameroon.</s></p></content></protolog>